09:16.335 --> 09:18.694
Can I just ask...?

09:18.695 --> 09:22.894
Can I just ask, why don't we
make that every week? Yes, I know.

09:22.895 --> 09:25.814
I want to be a karate expert.
I want an Interceptor.

09:25.815 --> 09:29.134
I want a moustache.
Well, there you go.

09:29.135 --> 09:34.575
Who here would like us to stop making
this rubbish and make that instead? Yes!

09:36.134 --> 09:37.773
